            <div class="col-md-9" id="bios">
              <p>He likes beer, reading, juggling, bowling, golf, baseball, hockey, and football. His favorite reading genres Sci-Fi, Fantasy, suspense, and true crime. As a hobby he likes building and fixing computers. He  attended technical college for networking, but taught himself all kinds of computer repair. Like OS repair, virus removal, and building desktop from parts.</p>
